title.narrative: West Africa Regional Communications Infrastructure Program

description.narrative: WARCIP seeks to increase the geographical reach of broadband networks and reducing the costs of communications services in West Africa. Under APL1-A, the objectives of the Projects,thus, are to increase the geographical reach of broadband networks and to reduce costs of communications services in the territory of Liberia and Sierra Leone.
